  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Thoracotomy is one of the most painful operation. Continuous thoracic epidural or&#xD;
      paravertebral analgesia are gold standard for postoperative pain. But both techniques require&#xD;
      skills. Spinal morphine is alternative simple method with less efficacy. Adding low dose&#xD;
      ketamine during intraoperative may be helpful in postoperative pain relief.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
